{"tid":1329244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［721] 咪撚再理罵戰 黑警 張超雄呢三方面既Post!","createTime":"2019-07-18T06:59:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T11:32:45.000Z","uid":17991,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"241483a3ae319642bc2344405b3cfd7a7a236e27","tid":1329244,"uid":17991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:59:21.000Z","msg":"從來干預到我地既<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">行動</span></span>既只係政府回應我地五大訴求同埋戰術調整<br />\n而我地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">心態</span>上都唔應該受呢三方面受影響<br />\n因此咪再理呢啲post，因為無人知佢背後有咩目的<br />\n勿忘初衷，勿忘義死士<br />\n從來我地既隊友只有我地身邊一齊出黎既人<br />\n黎緊721 唔可以俾人有機可乘令我地心態有變<br />\n一日未撤回訴求，一日永不罷休。"},{"pid":"b227467dca32c1329fbb56ada1bf0b8957c3ce18","tid":1329244,"uid":276066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:01:57.000Z","msg":"[7.21 遊行] 文宣集中地<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1329230\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1329230</a>"},{"pid":"4436409aea3d67e87fdbca23b2f5fb1ac59b48e5","tid":1329244,"uid":83025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BCXsaKV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBCXsaKV.png&h=24af622a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YpVEMig.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYpVEMig.png&h=2e79ac93&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"501adb52ce9bbedc9b48dcc636db0776378d4608","tid":1329244,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:12:32.000Z","msg":"無錯"},{"pid":"ec42079eefc3ed1b474be92190c54aecc953945d","tid":1329244,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:15:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>【Hongkongers! Assemble! 】</strong></span><br />\n光復香港！沒有暴民，只有暴政！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kVURRBwauKE\" data-sr-url=\"http